{"tid":384723,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有睇 奇葩說","createTime":"2017-09-02T14:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T02:40:22.000Z","uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e90c097212da1ed91f514fe40a1d33f08e71940d","tid":384723,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:22:22.000Z","msg":"討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n奇葩說係說話達人秀 每集會有一集辯題<br />\n各個方面除左政治都有<br />\n包括：（一啲我覺得唔錯既）<br />\n女性專屬停車位是否歧視？<br />\n「愚人水」要不要喝？<br />\n好朋友可不可以約（炮）？<br />\n親人身患絕症想放棄，應否鼓勵他繼續堅持？<br />\n是否願意做單親媽媽？<br />\n異地戀伴侶建議available 你接受嗎？<br />\n<br />\n好多切入角度都好新穎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之餘啲導師仲幫大家梳理思路同掃除盲點（有蔡康永！）<br />\n黃執中同陳銘係我最鍾意既辯手，兩個既睇法都好獨特<br />\n特別係黃執中好快就點得出問題本質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人有睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無睇既快啲去睇下，真心正，打開新世界"},{"pid":"b6a24235793c1fd60600f4ec7ae3d1d25d244a36","tid":384723,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe02464a06b0e1e82b9371e2109708699276482","tid":384723,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T20:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9457b4449385e5171e5e2e20c1b6bb9985bff94b","tid":384723,"uid":192589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:03:12.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfcddf58583050a56658398a0d84f9c51ac8deaf","tid":384723,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9457b4449385e5171e5e2e20c1b6bb9985bff94b","tid":384723,"uid":1